# SCRIPT: perf_status
#
# DESCRIPTION:
#
# Simple script to check the current status of performance timing and to allow
# us to switch timing on/off, clear log files, delete them etc.
#
# INFORMATION:
#
# None
#
# REVISION:
#
# $Revision: 1.21 $
